title: 85: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode: January Edition
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode: January Edition
description:
New year, new Trader Joe’s finds! In today’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying new food finds from the trader we call Joe! Finds like dips, burgers, dogs, cheese, and more! Plus, a find that’s so good, it got a 10 out of 10 on Lisa’s rating scale! And there’s a BREAKING CHEWS story that might affect something you buy at TJ’s! So sit back, relax, and enjoy the show. And when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the food finds mentioned in the episode!
